Articles.Content:
So I have been trying to open KSP for a while, and I keep getting stuck on this one file, the swept2 in the Wings. At first, it loaded in a flash, but now I keep getting stuck on it because I have the Before Kerbin mod, and I have been removing some saves, and it still doesn't help. Any ideas?

Edited October 5, 2017 by planet-creations

"but now I keep getting stuck on it because I have the Before Kerbin mod"

You've probably installed the mod incorrectly.. Make sure the version of the mod is the right version for your KSP version. Also make sure you have the dependencies of the mod, like Kopernicus.

This are just some guesses, if that doesn't solve the problem, please upload some logs like described here:

22 hours ago, planet-creations said:

So I have been trying to open KSP for a while, and I keep getting stuck on this one file, the swept2 in the Wings. At first, it loaded in a flash, but now I keep getting stuck on it because I have the Before Kerbin mod, and I have been removing some saves, and it still doesn't help. Any ideas?

You installed wrong, or you are out of ram. You have two options which makes my life as the mod author easier:

1. Join the planet modding discord and we can talk through real time chat amongst a group of planet modders - link is on my release threads

2. Submit your output log here.
